name: Inside Her Mind
description:
nside Her Mind;
is not just a piece of digital art creation, it is actually what is going on in my lovely partner Cansu's mind.
While I am working on my research, she sits by my side and talks about the deer and here I tried to visualize her mind, her worlds...
We worked almost 1 week together to complete this colorful new world.

Here is the result; 
We have a new hairy friend, it's name is Fernando. He likes licking ice cream and sleep all day. Although he walks a charming walk; he is not into flirting as much as he is into farting bubblegums in magical colors...

Süleyman and Ceren, helped us for music and some awesome fart effects.
